          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Constitutional Amendment</b></p> <p>This joint resolution proposes a constitutional amendment prohibiting the federal government, states, or places subject to their jurisdiction from denying persons the right to a fair and equal education. The amendment makes it the responsibility of the states, Indian tribes, and territories to provide a quality education to all persons.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2016-07-14T04:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
